// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0012 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 5cde27b7-83ae-51a8-a367-3dc91173091f

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:2023* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:7* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:8* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:9*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
